-- ft.page: `quote` and it's Usage

`-- quote` can be used as part of blog posts to highlight a quote from blogger.


-- pd.package: `quote`
name: fifthtry.github.io/bling/quote

To use these quotes on your web package, add below into `FPM.ftd` file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling/quote
\-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling/quote


-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your web package, add `quote` into your `.ftd` files:


-- ft.code: Basic Example: 
lang: ftd


\-- quote: Amit Upadhyay
label: CEO
avatar: $assets.files.amitu.jpg
logo: $assets.files.fifthtry.svg

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod 
tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.



-- quote: Amit Upadhyay
label: CEO
avatar: $assets.files.amitu.jpg
logo: $assets.files.fifthtry.svg

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod 
tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua..
















